CFSF with Bi-Stage Clearing Unit Characteristics

1. RPM: 10-15 rev/min
2. Inlet fluid gets filtered twice before entering calandria.
3. Rotation 
4. The base of CFSF contains micro membrane filtration cloth for providing  at most filtration eliminating the least possible adulteration.  
5.  CFSF maximizes the boundary contact which means increase in efficiency and lower steam feed required. 
